VENDORED SVG ASSETS — sources & licenses
==========================================

All SVGs here were rewritten to be self-contained and to use `currentColor` for
every stroke/fill, so they inherit the cover's palette (the cover sets `color`
to the palette ink/accent). No original hex colors were kept.

------------------------------------------------------------------
