------------------------------------------------------------------
Source : https://github.com/tabler/tabler-icons
Version fetched from CDN: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons (2026-07-07)
License: MIT (https://github.com/tabler/tabler-icons/blob/main/LICENSE)
Terms  : MIT is permissive — commercial use, modification (incl. recoloring and
         restroking), and redistribution are all allowed. No attribution is
         legally required; this NOTICE credits the source as good practice.
Modification made: dropped Tabler's transparent bounding-box <path>, stripped
         per-path stroke/fill overrides, set stroke-width 1.6, kept only `d=`
         so the shape inherits `stroke="currentColor"` from the root <svg>.

